{"title":"无梦的夜 Dreamless Night","date":"2020-05-24T17:12:22.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 25, 2020","L":"05/25/2020","MM-DD":"05-25"},"author":"WardZhou","thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/bear-2382779_640.jpg","link":"2020/05/25/DreamlessNight","comments":true,"tags":["他","诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.492Z","content":"<p>寥落的夜以继夜<br>\n苦涩的茶渗出幽香<span id=\"more\"></span><br>\n不甘地又<br>\n扔进两块方糖</p>\n<p>茶本不该甜<br>\n夜本不该甜<br>\n没有你的每一片时空<br>\n都是无尽的虚无</p>\n<p>至少我还拥有这份苦涩<br>\n和嘴边空留的甜</p>\n<p>再倒进半杯酒<br>\n我们间的咫尺似乎又近了</p>\n<p>我还有大把的夜<br>\n夜里还有我在想你<br>\n当我想你的时候最想你</p>\n<iframe src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=795637027&bvid=BV1tC4y1H7yz&cid=192966399&page=1\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"100%\" style=\"height: calc(25vh)\"> </iframe>","prev":{"title":"阳光","link":"2020/05/31/Sunshine"},"next":{"title":"轨道 Orbit","link":"2020/05/23/Orbit"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/05/25/DreamlessNight/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"WardZhou","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"110 words in 1 min"}